              "free_text": [
                " The two semiconductor detectors were mounted",
                "in a back-to-back arrangement at an angle of 90",
                "degrees relative to the beam direction. The energy",
                "calibration of the semiconductor detectors was",
                "obtained by observing fragments from the spontaneous",
                "fission of Cf252 and comparing the results to the",
                "double-velocity measurements of Whetstone."
              ]
